content:
Einstein Discovery in Tableau provides real-time predictions and improvements for Tableau data. It brings trusted predictions to worksheets, calculated fields, and flows with a no-code required environment.

Get Predictions in Tableau Dashboards: Integrate on-demand predictions from Einstein Discovery natively in Tableau dashboards.

Get Predictions in Tableau Calculated Fields: Select a prediction definition, generate a Tableau script, and copy it into a calculated field.

Embed Einstein Predictions in Tableau Flows: Use the Prediction step in Tableau Prep to include predictions directly into flows. Enrich flow output with predictions and optional improvements and top factors.
title: Getting Predictions in Tableau
